It's my last day in Milan here with @philippemodelparis. It has been an amazing experience so far. I can highly recommend coming to Milan during Milan Design Week and see all the creative design installations. I hope you followed and enjoyed my Instagram Stories Takeover on @philippemodelparis account. 
A big thank you to @philippemodelparis for having invited me to Milan and letting me share all these moments with you!
#philippemodel #2steps2italy #mdw2017

My last day here in Milan with @philippemodelparis has started. I still have time to explore the last hidden treasures of Milan Design Week and soak up some last inspiration.
While walking through the neighborhood of Brera I discovered this cute restaurant with brazilian/japanese inspired food. The decor was set to give a tropical beach vibe and it couldn't have been a better match for my Tucan sneakers!
Check @philippemodelparis Instagram Stories to discover my adventures on this last day in Milan!
#philippemodel #2steps2italy #mdw2017

Once you enter the Triennale di Milano you will immediately discover an enormous mosaic installation at the entrance. Of course I couldn't resist snapping my vision of it with my new @philippemodelparis sneakers.
#philippemodel #2steps2italy #mdw2017

Another exciting day ahead of me. I hope you are enjoying following my adventures on @philippemodelparis Instagram Stories. Stay tuned for more cool shoes and floors!!
#philippemodel #2steps2italy #mdw2017

I am excited to announce that I will be going to Milan on Monday with @philippemodelparis to discover their new store and find some cool new floors in the city. I will also be taking over their Instagram Stories next week and checking out Milan Design Week. If anyone has some cool recommendations on where to go and what to do in Milan and especially during MDW please leave a comment or send me a DM! Your tipps anf help are always highly appreciated! Enjoy your weekend and stay tuned for an exciting week in Milan!
